Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.00,0:00:17.00,Default,,0,0,0,,(Crickets chirp)
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.00,0:00:29.00,Default,,0,0,0,,(Industrial/Electrical Sounds)
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.00,0:00:35.00,Default,,0,0,0,,(Dripping Water)
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.00,0:01:53.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Guard: Oh it's you! You're not supposed to be here.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.00,0:01:58.00,Default,,0,0,0,,(Gun fire)
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.00,0:02:10.00,Default,,0,0,0,,(Blurred voices and music)
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.00,0:02:20.00,Default,,0,0,0,,(Alarm clock rings)
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.00,0:02:31.00,Default,,0,0,0,,(Bird song)
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.00,0:02:35.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Connor: (Groans)
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.00,0:02:48.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Connor: James get up. We're late.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.00,0:02:52.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Connor: (Sighs)
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.00,0:03:15.00,Default,,0,0,0,,James: Why'd we have to get so drunk on a Sunday night?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.00,0:03:30.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Connor: Do you remember that part last night where Amy got on the table and started to...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.00,0:03:33.00,Default,,0,0,0,,James: (Interrupts) Dude, that's my sister! Don't want to be reminded.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.00,0:03:41.00,Default,,0,0,0,,James: Where's all the food?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.00,0:03:48.00,Default,,0,0,0,,James: (Sighs)
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.00,0:03:51.00,Default,,0,0,0,,(Car horn honks)
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.50,0:03:53.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Connor: Come on. Let's go!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.00,0:04:05.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Amy: Come on guys, we're gonna be late!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.50,0:04:08.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Connor: Sure you're ok to drive after your stunt last night Amy?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.80,0:04:18.50,Default,,0,0,0,,James: Oh... Hi Matt.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.70,0:04:20.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Matt: You al'right?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.00,0:04:27.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Connor: Not getting the bus today?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.00,0:04:28.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Matt: Nope!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.50,0:04:35.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Amy: I saw him as I was driving past the shops and picked him up.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.50,0:04:36.50,Default,,0,0,0,,James: Oh ok.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.00,0:04:40.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Connor: So what's the rush anyway?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.50,0:04:42.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Amy: Some kind of emergency meeting.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.00,0:07:08.30,Default,,0,0,0,,James: What do you think this emergency meeting is about?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.30,0:07:11.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Amy: I don't know, but... it can't be that important.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.00,0:07:18.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Matt: All right, go on ahead guys. I'm going to go powder my nose.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.00,0:07:34.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Director General (DG): No! Dr. Niven LHC is the most important experiment of our time. I will not let unfounded theories...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.00,0:07:36.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Dr. Niven: (Interrupts) Unfounded?! Director, my results how that...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.40,0:07:43.00,Default,,0,0,0,,DG: (Interrupts) Inconclusive! Your results are inconclusive at best. No, you'll have plenty of time for measurements when you're down in the tunnel tonight.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.00,0:07:47.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Dr. Niven: Director we have to stop the LHC until we assess the danger.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.00,0:07:52.30,Default,,0,0,0,,DG: No Dr. Niven. Once we have fixed this problem the LHC will run again as usual.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.00,0:07:56.00,Default,,0,0,0,,DG: Find the Higgs is the highest priority.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.30,0:08:11.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Amy: Why is doctor Niven going into the tunnels?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.00,0:08:40.30,Default,,0,0,0,,James: Why do you think the Director General is here?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.10,0:08:42.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Matt: Maybe they made a black hole...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.00,0:08:52.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Lisa: (Very quiet) Sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.40,0:08:55.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Lisa: Hey.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.40,0:08:55.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Amy: Hey.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.40,0:08:57.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Lisa: So, did you recover from last night?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.50,0:08:59.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Amy: ...Yeah. You too?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.50,0:08:59.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Lisa: Mmmhmm.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.00,0:09:03.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Amy: Wait, aren't you supposed to be on your way to Barcelona by now?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.00,0:09:05.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Lisa: I might have missed my flight.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.00,0:09:06.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Amy: Oh no!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.00,0:09:19.00,Default,,0,0,0,,DG: Good morning! I am Professor Vacinski, Director General of CERN.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.00,0:09:24.00,Default,,0,0,0,,DG: This meeting has been called because last night there was an emergency beam dump.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.30,0:09:25.00,Default,,0,0,0,,(Crowd whispers furtively)
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.00,0:09:31.00,Default,,0,0,0,,DG: Here we see a monopole magnet in LHC Sector 7G.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.00,0:09:41.00,Default,,0,0,0,,DG: Beam sensors have detected an unknown event caused this magnet to quench and triggered an uncontrolled shut down.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.00,0:09:45.00,Default,,0,0,0,,DG: If this happens again the results could be catastrophic.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.30,0:09:55.00,Default,,0,0,0,,DG: Due to the special circumstances, Dr. Niven is taking a team into the LHC tunnel to investigate the cause and see what damage there is.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.00,0:10:00.00,Default,,0,0,0,,The LHC will be in shut down until at least the end of the week. 
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.50,0:10:07.00,Default,,0,0,0,,DG: Since Dr. Niven will not be available we will need 4 volunteers to be on shift in the control room.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.50,0:10:09.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Connor: We'll do it.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.30,0:10:10.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Amy: (Quietly) What are you doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.40,0:10:12.30,Default,,0,0,0,,DG: Ok, you four.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.00,0:10:16.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Lisa: Oh, I'm going to be at a conference in Barcelona.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.30,0:10:21.00,Default,,0,0,0,,DG: Uh, very well. You... you then!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.00,0:10:27.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Matt: Uh, I have an analysis note due this week so I'm not going to have time to do this.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.00,0:10:30.30,Default,,0,0,0,,DG: (Interrupting) The collider will be shut down. You can work in the control room.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.30,0:10:35.30,Default,,0,0,0,,DG: Report to the control room at 9pm. That is all everybody.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.10,0:10:39.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Lisa: Sucks to you guys!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.30,0:11:01.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Connor: Here you go.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.30,0:11:02.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Amy: Thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.50,0:11:05.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Connor: They don't looks like proton decay matrices.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.00,0:11:07.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Amy: Uh, no. 
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.20,0:11:16.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Amy: Dr. Niven has got me working on this Higgs Bioentanglement simulation.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.50,0:11:20.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Amy: Some company gave a lot of money to CERN and I get stuck working on it.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.00,0:11:22.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Amy: I have so much work to do.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.30,0:11:26.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Connor: Listen, are you ok after last night?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.30,0:11:28.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Amy: Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.55,0:11:30.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Connor: You and Matt...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.50,0:11:32.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Amy:  I don't know what you're talking about. Anyway, you jealous?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.00,0:11:39.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Amy: Oh... sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.00,0:11:44.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Amy: Listen, I better go. I've got a lot of work to do.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.40,0:12:12.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Amy: Oh I'm so tired. I can't even think about work right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.00,0:12:16.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Amy: I hope he doesn't expect me to remember anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.50,0:12:25.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Dr. Niven: Ah Lisa. Did you finish your talk?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.00,0:12:26.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Lisa: Yeah! Just in time.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.30,0:12:27.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Dr. Niven: I had every confidence in you.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.30,0:12:30.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Amy: Did you get a chance to look at my simulation?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.30,0:12:34.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Dr. Niven: Ah yes! A problem with the sympasomatic parameter lattice.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.00,0:12:37.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Dr. Niven: I think I found a way to express it differently.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.30,0:12:45.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Dr. Niven: I didn't implement it in my analysis code yet but you might like to try it.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.00,0:12:53.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Amy: It looks more complex though. I don't know if it will work on my laptop.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.00,0:12:55.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Dr. Niven: Well, we will deal with that later if we need to.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.00,0:12:56.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Amy: Ok, thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.00,0:13:03.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Dr. Niven: Anyway I have to prepare my team for going into the tunnels and look over Lisa's talk so I will talk to you later.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.00,0:13:09.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Dr. Niven: And Lisa, don't miss the plane again.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.30,0:13:10.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Lisa: I won't.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.00,0:13:33.30,Default,,0,0,0,,James: Hey guys, wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.50,0:13:37.30,Default,,0,0,0,,James: I'm waiting for someone.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.40,0:13:38.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Amy: Who?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.40,0:13:40.40,Default,,0,0,0,,James: Just... someone.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.00,0:13:43.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Matt: Ok, well, we're going to be late so...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.30,0:13:48.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Kate: Hi!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.00,0:14:01.00,Default,,0,0,0,,James: Everyone, this is my girlfriend Kate.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.00,0:14:05.00,Default,,0,0,0,,James: Kate, this is Matt and Connor
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.30,0:14:04.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Connor: Hi.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.00,0:14:06.30,Default,,0,0,0,,James: And my sister Amy.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.30,0:14:06.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Kate: Hi.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.30,0:14:08.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Amy: Nice to finally meet you.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.40,0:14:10.00,Default,,0,0,0,,James: Finally...? I didn't tell you...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.50,0:14:13.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Amy: Mum let it slip. I was waiting for you to tell me.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.00,0:14:17.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Kate: It's nice to finally meet you as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.00,0:14:18.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Amy: Are you coming with us?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.30,0:14:18.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Kate: I think so.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.00,0:14:19.00,Default,,0,0,0,,James: Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.30,0:14:19.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Amy: Ok.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.30,0:14:21.00,Default,,0,0,0,,James: Shall we go?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.23,0:14:26.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Connor: So um, why have you thrown your evening away to go on shift?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.00,0:14:31.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Kate: James was going to come meet me for dinner but he told that you guys had to...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.00,0:14:32.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Connor: Oh... sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.30,0:14:33.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Kate: It's ok, don't worry.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.00,0:14:38.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Matt: And how did James manage to convince you that vending machine food is going to be an acceptable substitute?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.00,0:14:47.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Amy: Shift can sometimes be boring, are you going to be ok?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.00,0:14:49.00,Default,,0,0,0,,James: I told her.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.40,0:14:49.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Kate: I insisted.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.00,0:15:04.00,Default,,0,0,0,,James: She's with me.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.00,0:15:14.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Kate: so are you guys physicists like James then?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.00,0:15:18.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Connor: Yeah but he works on the accelerator. The rest of us analyse the data.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.30,0:15:19.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Matt: Yeah, he is an engineer and we are real physicists.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.00,0:15:21.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Amy: (Sighs)
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.30,0:15:32.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Amy: So what do you do?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.00,0:15:33.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Kate: I'm a trainee nurse.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.00,0:15:42.00,Default,,0,0,0,,James: I hope you are not claustrophobic, it is a long way down.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.50,0:15:51.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Kate: (Coughs)
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.00,0:16:18.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Matt: Guys, I have thought of a joke.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.00,0:16:20.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Connor: Ugh another one?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.00,0:16:23.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Matt: So a chimpanzee and a sloth go down...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.00,0:16:30.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Matt: And then the chimpanzee is like "uh uh, starfish! Starfish!"
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.00,0:16:32.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Everyone: (Laughs)
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.00,0:16:48.00,Default,,0,0,0,,James: Do you want to watch "A Clockwork Orange"? I borrowed it from Amy.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.30,0:16:48.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Kate: Yep, sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.50,0:16:52.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Matt: That's a pretty deep film for a lowly engineer like yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.00,0:16:52.30,Default,,0,0,0,,James: (Laughs)
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.30,0:16:59.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Kate: You shouldn't let him talk to you like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.50,0:17:00.00,Default,,0,0,0,,James: He's only messing around.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.30,0:17:31.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Matt: Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.20,0:17:37.30,Default,,0,0,0,,James: So the accelerator boosts the beam of protons to almost the speed of light.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.00,0:17:42.00,Default,,0,0,0,,James: And then we collide them... here.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.50,0:17:45.00,Default,,0,0,0,,James: And then we detect what's made in the collision.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.30,0:17:56.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Amy: (Sighs loudly)
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.00,0:17:58.00,Default,,0,0,0,,James: What's up?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.30,0:18:00.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Amy: I thought I'd got it working!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.30,0:18:03.00,Default,,0,0,0,,James: Got what working.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.00,0:18:04.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Connor (off screen): Her Higgs simulation.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.00,0:18:06.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Kate: Her... what simulation?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.30,0:18:09.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Amy: My Higgs radiation simulation. 
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.30,0:18:13.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Matt: The "God" particle.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.30,0:18:17.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Amy: It's a particle that we're trying to make in the collider.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.30,0:18:23.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Amy: I'm supposed to be investigating how it acts on living tissue, but my programme just crashes every single time that it starts to look bad.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.00,0:18:26.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Connor: so what, you think Higgs radiation is dangerous?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.30,0:18:28.30,Default,,0,0,0,,
